statement.p:
Consider the function y=f(x) below.

  f(x) = \left\{
  \begin{array}{ll}
  10-x^2 \amp x \leqslant 3 \\
  4x-11 \amp 3 \lt x \\
  \end{array}
  \right.

Consider the function y=g(x) below.

  f(x) = \left\{
  \begin{array}{ll}
  3x+5 \amp x \leqslant 2 \\
  x^2+C \amp 2 \lt x \\
  \end{array}
  \right.

